# SPARSH DESIGN - Luxury Fashion Boutique ðŸ‘—

SPARSH DESIGN is a **full MERN stack luxury fashion boutique website**, built to deliver a modern, responsive, and elegant shopping experience. It includes both user and admin interfaces with real-time updates, categorized collections, and interactive animations.

---

## ðŸš€ Features

### ðŸ›ï¸ User Side

* Beautifully designed homepage with **hero banners** and **animated sections**.
* View **collections** (bridal, kidswear, custom designs, etc.) with categorized browsing.
* **Gallery** section displaying real-time image updates.
* **Book Appointment** for personalized styling.
* Mobile-friendly responsive layout.

### ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ’¼ Admin Side

* **Secure authentication** for admin login.
* Admin can **upload, categorize, and manage images**.
* Real-time updates to the **Gallery component** using Socket.IO.
* Clean, modern dashboard interface.

---

## ðŸ§© Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, ShadCN UI
**Backend:** Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose
**Real-Time Updates:** Socket.IO
**Authentication:** JSON Web Token (JWT)
**Hosting:** Vercel (Frontend) & Render (Backend)

