## âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Gokul11271/SPARSH-DESIGN.git
cd SPARSH-DESIGN
```

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

Create a `.env` file in the backend root:

```
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
PORT=5000
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
```

Start the server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

Server runs on **[http://localhost:5000](http://localhost:5000)** ðŸš€

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

Access frontend on **[http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173)** ðŸ’«

